  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_9_2913-2955",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2913-2955",
      "markText": "这两段全然不同的经历教会我，在共事之前，深入了解未来共事者的动力与动机是非常重要的。",
      "totalCount": 1568,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2913&rangeEnd=2955",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2913&rangeEnd=2955"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_10_4088-4166",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "4088-4166",
      "markText": "尽管我对前几年在本科和研究生阶段所做的研究项目全无好感，但通过这些项目，我才练就了技术能力与辨识能力，我现在才能够有实力做我自己真正在乎的、属于自己的研究。",
      "totalCount": 1152,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4088&rangeEnd=4166",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4088&rangeEnd=4166"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_7_7128-7196",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7128-7196",
      "markText": "相对于一个博士生（就是我！）花长时间设置Klee来找错误，Klee-UC更好用，因为它能在几分钟内自动找到所有的错误，不需任何额外设置。",
      "totalCount": 1054,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7128&rangeEnd=7196",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7128&rangeEnd=7196"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_7_8447-8500",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "8447-8500",
      "markText": "于是，我仍然让Dawson做我的导师，但是我离开了Klee项目组。我决定，从零开始，创造我自己的研究计划。",
      "totalCount": 936,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8447&rangeEnd=8500",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8447&rangeEnd=8500"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_9_12327-12379",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "12327-12379",
      "markText": "这段经历告诉我，背后有大人物支持，非常重要；在竞争激烈的学界中，想要被伯乐相中，光能做出好结果是不够的。",
      "totalCount": 896,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12327&rangeEnd=12379",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12327&rangeEnd=12379"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_4_1198-1213",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1198-1213",
      "markText": "不知道前人站在哪里，谈何创新。",
      "totalCount": 810,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1198&rangeEnd=1213",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1198&rangeEnd=1213"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_8_1086-1131",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1086-1131",
      "markText": "一定要积极和教授讨论，以找到你们彼此都感兴趣的研究项目；不论如何，都不要躲在自己的小世界里",
      "totalCount": 790,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1086&rangeEnd=1131",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1086&rangeEnd=1131"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_7_9020-9108",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "9020-9108",
      "markText": "最后，闭关科研的日子反而是我浪费时间最多的日子：我看电视剧，睡觉，在网上闲晃。和那些朝九晚五工作的同学不一样，我没有老板天天监视，于是我在自由幻想的海洋畅游，却完全看不到海岸。",
      "totalCount": 741,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=9020&rangeEnd=9108",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=9020&rangeEnd=9108"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_7_4430-4510",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4430-4510",
      "markText": "然而在读博士研究生时，研究是我唯一的工作，没有优秀的研究成果，就拿不到学位。于是我的心情完全和每天的研究进展紧密相关，而在那些日子里，研究进展真是慢得让我痛苦。",
      "totalCount": 663,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4430&rangeEnd=4510",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4430&rangeEnd=4510"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_9_6730-6767",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6730-6767",
      "markText": "如果Dawson能和一个自己年轻时期的克隆人一起工作，进展想必会迅猛得多！",
      "totalCount": 640,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6730&rangeEnd=6767",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6730&rangeEnd=6767"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_12_4039-4087",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "4039-4087",
      "markText": "上天给了我很多机会，我很幸运。但是如果没能主动去抓住这些机会，我也就不会踏上最后一年的冒险之旅。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=4039&rangeEnd=4087",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=4039&rangeEnd=4087"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_9_12971-13025",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "12971-13025",
      "markText": "相比而言，在学校时，理论上，只要我头脑是清醒的，就可以一刻不停地工作，这样一来，我时常担忧自己是否足够努力。",
      "totalCount": 629,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12971&rangeEnd=13025",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12971&rangeEnd=13025"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_13_1663-1760",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1663-1760",
      "markText": "相反，在写博士论文时，我为撰写综述所做的阅读就非常有效率，这是因为这时读论文，我有非常明确的目标，而我的阅读也紧密围绕了这个目标：找出同领域中的“竞争者”，从他们的文章中吸收好的点子，为己所用。",
      "totalCount": 624,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1663&rangeEnd=1760",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1663&rangeEnd=1760"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_9_13574-13630",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "13574-13630",
      "markText": "由于这两次经历的结果有天壤之别，而我的智力又没什么变化，因此我实习项目成功的最大功臣，莫过于微软公司与Tom了。",
      "totalCount": 612,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=13574&rangeEnd=13630",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=13574&rangeEnd=13630"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_9_2420-2479",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2420-2479",
      "markText": "经过这样的事后反省，我现在能明白，项目失败，是因为参与者之间志不同道不合。可惜当时，我没有足够智慧预见这样的失败结果。",
      "totalCount": 578,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2420&rangeEnd=2479",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2420&rangeEnd=2479"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_9_4024-4055",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4024-4055",
      "markText": "每天看不到明显的进展时，想要充满干劲地继续科研，真的非常困难。",
      "totalCount": 561,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4024&rangeEnd=4055",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4024&rangeEnd=4055"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_7_10533-10601",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "10533-10601",
      "markText": "我博士第一年被Klee“研”磨了四个月，留下了巨大心里阴影，自己闭关了十周，毫无目的，博一快结束时，反而些许积极。这，就是我的博一生涯。",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10533&rangeEnd=10601",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10533&rangeEnd=10601"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_7_8013-8053",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "8013-8053",
      "markText": "实习内容和我感兴趣的研究不全相关，但我一点都不在乎。我只是想要远离斯坦福几个月。",
      "totalCount": 528,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8013&rangeEnd=8053",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8013&rangeEnd=8053"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300057858_10_7770-7842",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "7770-7842",
      "markText": "对每个在那段艰难时光中帮助我的人，我都心存感激。他们明知道帮助我这个陌生博士生，除了我的祝福其它什么都换不来。尽管这样，他们还是慷慨地施以援手。",
      "totalCount": 527,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057858&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7770&rangeEnd=7842",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd32c90813ab7d19g0188aa?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7770&rangeEnd=7842"
    },
